Text: "There is a young woman who is basically  decides to take off from everything\
  \ she knows university her job. An opening a brand new chapter in her life.  When\
  \ she first gets to Portugal she learns about her family\u2018s history unknowingly\
  \ to her and how I could be traced almost 155 years. She talks with the locals experiences\
  \ the food thrives in the music culture there. Sitting in the small hideaway caf\xE9\
  \u2019s enjoying the green wine of the season. Finding love going through heartbreak\
  \ experiencing new friendships opening up yourself more to every possibility that\
  \ could happen each and every day."
